<paragraph id="8BDE36D83130FFE3367BFB12FBD1513D" blockId="9.[264,1325,817,1283]" pageId="9" pageNumber="48">The specimen from Alabama (deposited in the Cambridge University Museum of Zoology) is the first record of this species for the Nearctic Region</paragraph>
